      "pattern": "AよりBの方が～です",
      "explanation": "Used to compare two things. B is more ~ than A.",
      "examples": [
        {"jp": "中国より日本の方が大きいです", "en": "Japan is bigger than China (incorrect example, but pattern shown)"},
